CHB_0.05cM_Mb <- fread('altai_1kg_CHB_1.LOD4.0.05cM.bed', select = 1:3, col.names = c('ID','strt','end')) %>%
                    summarise(sum(end-strt)/1000000) %>% as.numeric()

CHB_50kb_Mb <- fread('Altai2013pub.CHB_1.LOD4.50K.filterAFRDeni.bed', select = 1:3, col.names = c('ID','strt','end')) %>%
                    summarise(sum(end-strt)/1000000) %>% as.numeric()

CHB_0.05cM_50kb_calls_MB <- fread(cmd = 'bedops --intersect altai_1kg_CHB_1.LOD4.0.05cM.bed Altai2013pub.CHB_1.LOD4.50K.filterAFRDeni.bed', 
                                   col.names = c('ID','strt','end')) %>%
                            summarise(sum(end-strt)/1000000) %>% as.numeric()






grid.newpage()
draw.pairwise.venn(
  area1 = as.integer(CHB_0.05cM_Mb),
  area2 = as.integer(CHB_50kb_Mb),
  cross.area = as.integer(CHB_0.05cM_50kb_calls_MB),
  category = c('CHB_0.05cM_MB','CHB_50kb_MB'),
  fill = c('red','dodgerblue3'),
  ext.text = FALSE,
  cat.cex=2,
  cat.fontface='bold',
  cat.default.pos = 'text',
  cat.just = list(c(0.7,-1.0), c(0.5,-1.0)),
  fontface = 'bold',
  cex=2,
  print.mode = 'raw',
  alpha=c(0.6, 0.9)
)

setwd('~/DATALab/NeanderthalSeq/IBDmix/GenomicDistance_test')

CHB_0.05cM_50kb_intersect <- fread(cmd = 'bedops --intersect altai_1kg_CHB_1.LOD4.0.05cM.bed Altai2013pub.CHB_1.LOD4.50K.filterAFRDeni.bed', 
                                   col.names = c('ID','strt','end')) 

CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo <- fread(cmd = 'bedops --element-of 1 altai_1kg_CHB_1.LOD4.0.05cM.bed Altai2013pub.CHB_1.LOD4.50K.filterAFRDeni.bed',
                            col.names = c('ID','strt','end', 'cM_len','bp_len','cM_Mb_ratio'))

CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo <- fread(cmd = 'bedops --not-element-of 1 altai_1kg_CHB_1.LOD4.0.05cM.bed Altai2013pub.CHB_1.LOD4.50K.filterAFRDeni.bed',
                            col.names = c('ID','strt','end', 'cM_len','bp_len','cM_Mb_ratio'))



CHB_50kb_0.05cM_eo <- fread(cmd = 'bedops --element-of 1 Altai2013pub.CHB_1.LOD4.50K.filterAFRDeni.bed altai_1kg_CHB_1.LOD4.0.05cM.bed',
                            col.names = c('ID','strt','end', 'LOD_score','bp_len'))

CHB_50kb_0.05cM_neo <- fread(cmd = 'bedops --not-element-of 1 Altai2013pub.CHB_1.LOD4.50K.filterAFRDeni.bed altai_1kg_CHB_1.LOD4.0.05cM.bed ',
                            col.names = c('ID','strt','end', 'LOD_score','bp_len'))



CHB.a <- ggplot() +
  theme_classic() +
  #geom_density(data = CHB_0.05cM_all, aes(x=log(cM_len), y = ..count../nrow(CHB_0.05cM_all)), alpha=0.5, fill='green') +
  geom_density(data = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo, aes(x=log(cM_len), y =..count.., fill = 'CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo'), alpha=0.5) +
  geom_density(data = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo, aes(x=log(cM_len), y = ..count.., fill = 'CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo'), alpha=0.5) +
  ggtitle('CHB_0.05cM_50kb') +
  scale_fill_brewer(type = 'div', palette = 'Dark2') +
  theme()

CHB.b <- ggplot() +
  theme_classic() +
  geom_density(data = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo, aes(x=log(bp_len), y =..count.., fill = 'CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo'), alpha=0.5) +
  geom_density(data = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo, aes(x=log(bp_len), y = ..count.., fill = 'CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo'), alpha=0.5) +
  
  geom_density(data = CHB_50kb_0.05cM_eo, aes(x=log(bp_len), y =..count.., fill = 'CHB_50kb_0.05cM_eo'), alpha=0.5) +
  geom_density(data = CHB_50kb_0.05cM_neo, aes(x=log(bp_len), y = ..count.., fill = 'CHB_50kb_0.05cM_neo'), alpha=0.5) +
  
  annotate(geom = "text", label = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo %>% summarise(sum(bp_len)/1000000) %>% as.numeric(), x = 9, y = 1000) +
  annotate(geom = "text", label = CHB_50kb_0.05cM_neo %>% summarise(sum(bp_len)/1000000) %>% as.numeric(), x = 11, y = 2000) +
  annotate(geom = "text", label = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo %>% summarise(sum(bp_len)/1000000) %>% as.numeric(), x = 13.5, y = 1000) +
  
  ggtitle('CHB_0.05cM_50kb') +
  scale_fill_brewer(type = 'div', palette = 'Dark2') +
  theme()

CHB.c <- ggplot() +
  theme_classic() +
  geom_density(data = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo, aes(x=log(cM_Mb_ratio), y =..count.., fill = 'CHB_0.05cM_50kb_eo'), alpha=0.5) +
  geom_density(data = CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo, aes(x=log(cM_Mb_ratio), y = ..count.., fill = 'CHB_0.05cM_50kb_neo'), alpha=0.5) +
  ggtitle('CHB_0.05cM_50kb') +
  scale_fill_brewer(type = 'div', palette = 'Dark2') +
  theme()

grid.arrange(CHB.a, CHB.b, CHB.c)
